captions.text:
- Why, hello everyone,
my name is Tyler Oakley

and today I am going
to dive into something
purely for YouTube research.
I don't know anything about this.
I am talking about the Kim Kardashian
Hollywood app game thing.
Let's do this.
So I am going to go search for the app.

Okay, so I type in Kim and
it's the first thing that

pops up, so clearly
this is a popular thing.
I fucking hate having to enter my fucking
Apple store shit password.
Yes.
Okay, it is officially downloading.
And apparently Kim Kardashian has already

made $85 million from this
app, which is mind blowing

because basically somebody
richer than all of us

made more than any of
us will ever make in our

lifetime providing us with
an experience where we

get to feel like we're rich
while we're actually poor.
Thanks, Kim.
It's done downloading.
Do I open it, do I dare?
I'm doing it, I have clicked the button.
It's happening.
(app noises)
Literally calm the fuck down.
Do I want push notifications?

This is like saying okay,
well, would I like to get

addicted to cocaine after
trying it for the first time?
Yes.
Okay, so --
(upbeat music)
Literally shh, quiet down.
What is this megamix?

Okay, I get to pick if
I'm a guy or a girl.

That's pretty gender
binary, but okay, I'm a guy.

They have misspelled the
word customize with a K.

I'm going to assume it's
because they're fucking idiots.

Before you were famous,
you were new to Hollywood.
Oh my god, this is kind of like my story.
I'm cute.
I need everyone to know that I am cute.

So far I am loving this
game because it provides me

with an experience where I
get to fucking fold clothes.
What are these lightning bolts?
Okay, I'm leaving the store.
(gasps) Kim!
Oh my God. (laughs)
She's literally in the game?
She looks great.

Oh my god, I just touched a
bike and a money fell out.

That's not how life
works, but I will take it.
I clicked a bird and a money fell out.
(phone ringing)
Kim, Kim Kardashian is calling!

Hey, it's Kim, I just
wanted to let you know that
you're all set to come by the -- oh.
(gasps)
I've leveled up.

She keeps telling me to dress
to impress and I'm like,

bitch, my whole aesthetic
is dressing to impress.
If you need to remind me, you haven't
looked me up and down yet.
Oh my god, I can buy a new haircut?
(gasps) It's so cute!
It's got shaved sides.
I'm 100% in for it.

Yes, I want to buy it, I
bought it, I bought it,

I bought it, bought it,
bought it, bought it.
I have no money left.
Should I have spent my money on a haircut?
Probably not.
But damn I look fucking good.
I would fuck me.
Now, I'm not really sure what's happening
in this game right now.
I have no clue what I'm trying to do
or what I'm trying to achieve.

It says I need to take
a bus to meet up with
Kim Kardashian, but that seems so fucking
not Kim Kardashian of me.
Oh my god, you're Kim Kardashian's friend.
What's your name again?
(gasps) I get to say my name?
@Tyler Oakley with an @ symbol.

Kim Kardashian is surprising
me with a photo shoot?

Oh my god, oh my god,
I look so fucking good.

I leveled up, level three,
get on my fucking level.
I need six more starts to go mint.

Well that's fucking ridiculous,
I want to go mint now.
Bitch, let me be me.
I don't really know what's going on.
Kim wants to talk to me again because
she's a needy fucking bitch.

Now I need you to know
that I have absolutely no

clue what's going on, but I
can't stop just clicking things.

I don't know if that's part
of the appeal of the game.
But it's working.

Okay, so I don't mean to
call a bitch out, but like,
why won't Simon stop calling me?
Who the fuck is Willow Pape?

Okay, so this is fun and
all, but at what point
do I get to make a sex tape?

Because I feel like I
was promised something
with the name Kim Kardashian.

And given that this is
a Kim Kardashian game,

I'm looking specifically
for some Illuminati shit.
And I feel like I'm seeing it.

Honestly, I feel like I
shouldn't be getting into this
game because in my youth I had a problem.
I would play games and I would play
video games like all of my life.

I would get grounded and
they would take away my

keyboard because that's how
addicted I was to video games.

And it even got to the
point where I would ask for

my birthday for nothing
of substance except for
24 hours of uninterrupted video games.

And I feel like if I
continue down this dark

and lonely path of Kim
Kardashian Hollywood,
I will get to that point again.
I feel like I need to just put it down.

Do I wait for it to give
me a push notification

or just say fuck it and
get back into the game?
What else do I have to do today?

What else do I have to do
with the rest of my life?

Why not just end this video
and go play more of the game?
Okay, it's been fun y'all.

If you play the Kim
Kardashian game, let me know

what you love and hate about
it in the comments below.

And if you like this video, be
sure to give it a thumbs up.
I think we can get 150,000 likes.

Last time I said 100,000,
y'all blew it out of the water

in one day, but I think
150,000, y'all can do it.
Let me see what y'all can do.

If you'd like to see my
latest Q&A, click right there.

If you want to see my latest
Friday video click right there.

If you want to be my person of
the week, click right there.

Get something real cute
and send me a picture
of you being cute with it on Twitter
and you might be featured right there.
And be sure to subscribe right there for
new videos every Tuesday and Friday.

And we are, like I said,
getting dangerously close

to 5 million, so I am
just like, you know what?

Let's do this, let's
blow right past there.

Introduce me to your friends,
your family, your lover,
Willow Pape, anybody, truly.
But that is all I have for you guys today.
I hope you have a fabulous life
and I will see you guys next time, later.

I feel like downloading
this game was a big mistake.
Goodbye forever.
